commit.message: [dist] Added public folder by default. Bumped to v0.2.9.
[test dist] Add request and vows to dev dependencies

Merge pull request #8 from nodejitsu/404-pages

[api] On 404, attempt to serve file /404.html
[fix] Will now handle case properly where no 404.html exists
[fix] remove vendor/ using bundleDeps and correcting .gitignore

[minor api] Assign created http server to a property

It makes using socket.io/dnode way easier.

Merge pull request #4 from travisperson/master

[fix] Root url links broken
If req.url was set to `/` it cause the links to think they were pointing to a different domain and the root urls would break.
[revert] Bad option parsing code. Force pushing v0.2.3
[dist] [fix] Patched node-static autoIndex bug. Bumped to v0.2.3
[bin] Moved argument parsing and colors to bin/
[dist] Exposed main script. Bumped to v0.2.1
[refactor] Moved argument parsing and help from bin/ to lib/
